===Noun===
'''Sukkot'''
# [[Jewish]] [[festival]] lasting eight days, celebrating the [[harvest]] and commemorating the passage through the wilderness; held the 15th day of the month of [[Tishri]], it is also called the [[Feast of Tabernacles]].

